diff --git a/CHANGES.rst b/CHANGES.rst
index 540bbe2..582457b 100644
--- a/CHANGES.rst
+++ b/CHANGES.rst
@@ -59,6 +59,13 @@ Unreleased
 -   If help is shown because ``no_args_is_help`` is enabled (defaults to ``True``
     for groups, ``False`` for commands), the exit code is 2 instead of 0.
     :issue:`1489` :pr:`1489`
+-   Fix shell completion so that contexts created while resolving the
+    command path are properly closed, preventing resource warnings for
+    things like open ``click.File`` handles.
+-   Add ``max_resources`` parameter to ``Context`` to limit the number of
+    resources that can be registered with ``Context.with_resource()``
+    across a context and its children, raising a ``RuntimeError`` if the
+    limit is exceeded.
 
 
 Version 8.1.8
